DEV README

Describe the goal of the application and value to a user
    This is an application inspired by the Law's field guide to California wildflowers,
    which I have used throughout my travels in the Sierra Nevada. This 
    app allows users to view wildflowers with details, sort and filter the flowers 
    to help them find what they are looking for, and add the flower to their 
    personal field journal to remember what they have seen outside. 

